#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Intro\n"
"-----\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:19
msgid ""
"With the bootlogo patch from SuSE you can get a nice logo instead of the "
"lilo prompt. This patch will help you."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Requirements\n"
"------------\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You nead:\n"
" - lilo 21.7 [1]\n"
" - SuSE's bootlogo patch [2]\n"
" - a 640x480 256color pcx graphic [3]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:31
msgid ""
"I found the sources of the patch for lilo (should also work with 21.6 and "
"21.6.1) on my SuSE 7.1 source CDs.  The author is Steffen Winterfeldt "
"<wfeldt@suse.de>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:33
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Installation\n"
"------------\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:40
msgid ""
"Decompress lilo and aply the patch: $ tar xvzf lilo-21.7.tar.gz $ bunzip2 "
"lilo-gfx-21.7.patch.bz2 $ cd lilo-21.7 $ patch -i ../lilo-gfx-21.7.patch"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:45
msgid "Build and install lilo: $ make $ su $ make install"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:50
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Generate the bootlogo:\n"
"$ mklilomsg --logo1 lfsbscreen.pcx 120 20 23 60 290 5 5 4 \\\n"
"  0x13 000000 111111 000000 > message \n"
"$ cp message /boot\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:56
msgid ""
"[ Could somebody find out how to use the xor rgb value at the end of "
"parameters ? It defines the color of the scrollbar but i got only rubish on "
"my own picture :o( mklilomsg.c has also two hidden flags (special and shade) "
"but none of them won't work for me. ]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:59
msgid "Edit /etc/lilo.conf: lilo.conf should read something like this"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:68
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"boot    = /dev/hde\n"
"vga     = normal\n"
"read-only\n"
"menu-scheme = Wg:kw:Wg:Wg\n"
"lba32\n"
"prompt\n"
"timeout = 80\n"
"message = /boot/message\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: origin/bootlogo.txt:70
msgid "Then start /sbin/lilo and reboot :o)"
msgstr ""

